trade.mtmSensitivityAnalysis: The contract includes an MTM sensitivity analysis, which shows the changes in the MTM due to parallel shifts in the USD SOFR-COMPOUND curve.
trade.levelOfPricingVariablesAndImpactOfVariab: The contract includes a level of pricing variables, which are used to determine the price of the contract.
trade.representations: Each party represents to the other party that it is acting for its own account and has made its own independent decisions to enter into this contract.
trade.acceptanceAndAgreement: The contract is accepted and agreed upon by Party B.

trade.lot: The contract is for a single trade lot.

account.collateral: The contract includes an independent amount of USD 284,693,760, which is paid by Party B to Party A.
